display_long_description:
Create complexly colorful **domino topples** in this sandbox mixed-reality experience, with new updates **every month**. Place, curve, and build amazing domino creations while channeling your inner domino artist✨

Discord 😙: https://discord.com/invite/xAX9hJZSzM

# NEW April '25 Update: ✨ Magic Touch ✨ Update
We're introducing a whole new feature called Magic Touch! 

[media]

# Key Features
- Place, curve, and build domino reactions
- Your creations are saved over multiple sessions
- Choose from vibrant domino colors

# Tips
Pinch with your hands facing down to create dominos, and turn your palm up to access your reset button and in-game menu! 

# You're Amazing
We are so thankful for our early access supporters! Don't forget to join our discord here to be a part of the Topple community: https://discord.com/invite/xAX9hJZSzM
